WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.110
What about Si Lei? How dare you not embarrass those people?

2
00:00:04.330 --> 00:00:06.310
I'll hit you if you dare to bully Xiaoyu again

3
00:00:06.310 --> 00:00:08.530
I'll make you regret living here.

4
00:00:08.670 --> 00:00:11.280
Where's Si Lei? You're such a ruthless stickman.

5
00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:14.340
Don’t forget that I was your wife back then

6
00:00:14.340 --> 00:00:16.880
You have so much love now that you dare to bully me like this, right?

7
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.440
Hey Zhang Yang, if someone bullies you, bring someone over immediately.

8
00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:28.390
Don't forget to try it with my husband. Just say something casually.

9
00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:31.220
I can only kick you away and do this for the rest of my life.

10
00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:34.700
Lin Xiaoshe is just always impulsive

11
00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:43.450
How about talking about it?

12
00:00:43.450 --> 00:00:45.260
Look at you like this

13
00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:48.840
It's still a matter of courtesy, as if we've already negotiated a contract

14
00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:11.280
It means there is no success

15
00:01:12.430 --> 00:01:14.550
Xiaoyu, she can't go with you

16
00:01:16.710 --> 00:01:22.880
Now lock yourself out of your mind

17
00:01:25.240 --> 00:01:26.760
Aren’t you harming the monks?

18
00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:29.440
On the surface, you see people communicating with each other

19
00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:32.380
Losing peace of mind during competition

20
00:01:33.300 --> 00:01:35.160
Will you become a monk now?

